# External Documentation Index

> A comprehensive map of ALL documentation files scattered across project codebases. This creates the "hub" that connects _meta.notes to every doc in the workspace.

---

## Why This Matters

Obsidian's Graph view shows disconnected nodes when docs don't link to each other. Since we can't edit files in codebases to link BACK to _meta.notes, we solve this by:

1. **Indexing** every doc that exists in codebases
2. **Linking** to them from _meta.notes using relative paths
3. **Categorizing** by project and document type

